Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.64,0:00:07.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to live in a world of peace\Nwithout conflict, like the one I dreamed of.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.88,0:00:19.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't be patient any longer\NThere are things I must say
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.84,0:00:23.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,At the evening bus stop\Non the way home
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.08,0:00:25.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I Wave to those sunken shoulders,\NBye Bye Bye
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.60,0:00:31.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Got to show your Fighting Pose, Oh! Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.84,0:00:37.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That world I dreamed of\NIs peaceful every day, without any conflict.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.92,0:00:40.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But in reality,\Nthere are troubles every day
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.40,0:00:44.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And sometimes I regret,\Nthese Rolling days
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.48,0:00:55.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Lies probably have little meaning
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.36,0:01:02.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,~All my loving\NOtherwise, how can I go on?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.12,0:01:08.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,A Sweet Love I dreamed of\Nwhere lovers search for a hideaway
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.92,0:01:11.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But in reality,\Nthe days we can't meet
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.84,0:01:19.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on; but we still believe,\Nthese Rolling days
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.12,0:01:25.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We may stumble, but Way to go!!\NYeah!! Yeah!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.68,0:01:27.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,A mud-caked Rolling star!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.41,0:01:33.41,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Soul Reapers...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.17,0:01:36.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They are the spiritual guardians\Nof the World of the Living.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.37,0:01:40.33,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They are the balancers\Nwho keep a close eye
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.37,0:01:43.37,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,on the countless souls, good and evil,\Nthat fill this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.41,0:01:47.73,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Aizen, who has brought chaos\Nupon the Soul Society,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.77,0:01:49.33,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,has begun to set his plan in motion.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.17,0:01:53.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Arrancars, created by Aizen\Nusing the Hogyoku,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.57,0:01:57.41,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,a material that removes the boundaries\Nbetween Soul Reapers and Hollows,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.45,0:01:59.13,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,appear in Karakura Town.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.57,0:02:00.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Bankai!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.05,0:02:09.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo prepares to battle\NUlquiorra and Yammy,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.69,0:02:11.81,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,sent to Karakura Town by Aizen,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.85,0:02:14.41,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,but the voice of the Hollow\Nwithin him
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.45,0:02:16.57,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,makes it impossible for him to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.85,0:02:22.45,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo is saved by\NUrahara and Yoruichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.29,0:02:25.57,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll report to Lord Aizen...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.61,0:02:30.49,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,that the wannabe Soul Reaper\Nhe has set his eyes on...is trash.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.53,0:02:32.45,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Not even worth killing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.73,0:02:36.29,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all because I'm weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.69,0:02:41.33,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what I can do\Nother than apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.37,0:02:49.85,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo! How you doing, Ichigo?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.41,0:02:56.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Renji?! Ikkaku?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.17,0:03:00.41,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yumichika, Rangiku...Toshiro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.73,0:03:03.73,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Captain Hitsugaya to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.93,0:03:07.37,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What...are you all doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.36,0:03:09.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Orders from above.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.72,0:03:11.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We were ordered to enter\Nthis world to prepare
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.00,0:03:14.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,for a full-on battle\Nwith the Arrancars,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.72,0:03:17.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and join up with\Nthe Substitute Soul Reaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.92,0:03:20.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Arran...? What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.32,0:03:27.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh...? Were you fighting without knowing\Nwho your opponents were?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.52,0:03:30.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.04,0:03:33.31,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.68,0:03:36.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's those guys who beat you up\Nthe other day!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.04,0:03:48.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.26,0:03:55.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Kuchiki...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.66,0:03:58.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a sec...\NShe just came through the window?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.22,0:04:01.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, she hasn't been in school\Nfor a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.86,0:04:04.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot... This has nothing to do\Nwith her not coming to school!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.34,0:04:07.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But...who the heck is that\Nredhead and skinhead?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.58,0:04:17.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the hell was that for, Rukia?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.42,0:04:19.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.10,0:04:21.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why you--!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.14,0:04:25.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that sorry look?!\NCome with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.74,0:04:29.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew this would happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.10,0:04:33.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. He's always so much trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.50,0:04:38.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that look on his face would\Nmake anyone want to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.50,0:04:39.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.66,0:04:42.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that gloomy look on\Nhis face was pretty stimulating.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.78,0:04:43.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.82,0:04:45.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing to get stimulated by!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.34,0:04:47.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't asking you for\Nyour opinion, Yumichika.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.98,0:04:50.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Then who were you asking?!\NIkkaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.66,0:04:52.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.46,0:04:55.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, you guys...\Nquiet down, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.14,0:04:56.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... Take a look at that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.50,0:04:58.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with Kurosaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.42,0:05:00.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he faint?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.46,0:05:04.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no... Isn't he dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.54,0:05:06.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you,\Nthose guys are bad news.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.14,0:05:09.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,With that red hair and those tattoos...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.26,0:05:13.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let them bother you, Renji.\NIt's just human silly talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.06,0:05:17.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,A blonde with big boobs and\Na silver-haired elementary student...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.14,0:05:21.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,A bob-haired narcissist and\Na baldy with a wooden sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.78,0:05:22.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.94,0:05:23.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.30,0:05:27.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Who just called me "baldy"?\NStep up...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.38,0:05:30.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better not let it bother you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.58,0:05:32.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just human silly talk, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.26,0:05:38.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it right there!\NI'll slice you to ribbons!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.74,0:05:40.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help you out, Ikkaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.22,0:05:43.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Can someone take over\Nthis job, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.14,0:05:50.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Rukia! Where do you think\Nyou're taking me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.42,0:05:52.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shush! Just shut up and run!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.26,0:05:57.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! There!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.78,0:06:04.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's here...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.90,0:06:15.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! A Hollow?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.34,0:06:18.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Go get 'im!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.54,0:06:19.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.82,0:06:27.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.42,0:06:40.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.82,0:06:56.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!\NHurry up and fight him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.82,0:07:00.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You call that fighting?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.54,0:07:01.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.66,0:07:05.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Normally, you wouldn't have\Nany trouble at all
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.36,0:07:07.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,defeating a Hollow like this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.46,0:07:10.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit complaining.\NYou don't have to tell me what to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.34,0:07:25.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you... I'm gonna...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.42,0:07:31.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting closer for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.42,0:07:35.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If I keep getting closer like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.02,0:07:40.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll swallow you up...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.22,0:07:42.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,- Then...\N- Stop! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.86,0:07:44.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,...you'll disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.14,0:07:56.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.42,0:08:00.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since you got beaten\Nby the Arrancars,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.42,0:08:02.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,you haven't transformed into\Na Soul Reaper, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.50,0:08:04.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you so afraid of?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.34,0:08:06.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.02,0:08:14.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They got Chad! They got Inoue!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.34,0:08:16.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.34,0:08:18.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you such a sorry person
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.50,0:08:21.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,that you'd lose heart over\Nsomething like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.30,0:08:24.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you afraid of losing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.38,0:08:27.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you afraid because\Nyou can't protect your comrades?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.34,0:08:34.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Or is it...that you're afraid\Nof the Hollow within you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.66,0:08:41.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're afraid of losing,\Njust become stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.46,0:08:47.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're afraid because\Nyou cannot protect your comrades,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.34,0:08:48.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,just become stronger,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.50,0:08:50.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and swear to them that\Nyou will protect them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.18,0:08:54.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're afraid of the Hollow\Nwithin you,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.58,0:08:57.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,then become stronger\Nuntil you're able to destroy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.34,0:09:01.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if no one else believes in you,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.94,0:09:04.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,just beat your chest and\Nshout that pledge!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.62,0:09:09.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the kind of man\Nyou are in my heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.90,0:09:30.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're noisy...both of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.74,0:09:34.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.50,0:09:48.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Inoue...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.82,0:09:52.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kuchiki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.86,0:09:55.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! It's been a while!\NOr...maybe not...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.38,0:09:58.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You've gotten over your injuries?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.70,0:10:01.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... Thanks to you, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.62,0:10:04.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No... I didn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.74,0:10:08.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How long can you stay here\Nthis time?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.86,0:10:10.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you about that later.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.38,0:10:11.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.46,0:10:18.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.14,0:10:22.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Inoue...I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.34,0:10:28.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I was so weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.46,0:10:33.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.22,0:10:40.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I...will get stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.94,0:10:45.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get stronger...\Nand next time, I swear...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.06,0:10:48.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I will protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.90,0:10:59.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness...\NHe's back to his usual self.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.38,0:11:05.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you... Kurosaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.02,0:11:10.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Kuchiki...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.50,0:11:13.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.94,0:11:25.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you, it's the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.54,0:11:28.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If you mix ginger ale and\Nlactic acid soda,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.18,0:11:30.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,two parts to one,\Nat that beverage bar...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.38,0:11:31.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.54,0:11:34.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll taste like hair tonic!\NIsn't that amazing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.74,0:11:37.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Isn't that amazing?\NJust leave it to you, Mr. Asano.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.10,0:11:39.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably your tongue...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.66,0:11:41.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Why're you suddenly\Nso formal?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.10,0:11:44.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Was I so irritating that you wanted\Nto put some distance between us?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.34,0:11:48.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...Mizuiro! Don't ignore me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.86,0:11:53.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Our classroom seems\Na little noisy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.30,0:11:55.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Yeah, you're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.42,0:11:59.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! I'll go and scout the area!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.70,0:12:06.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Who in the world is\Nstirring things up without me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.26,0:12:07.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.38,0:12:13.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What the heck are\Nyou looking at?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.22,0:12:17.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll grind you up, make meatballs,\Nfry you crisp
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.14,0:12:18.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,into a minced fish and\Neat you up! Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.02,0:12:22.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit it will you, Baldy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.82,0:12:25.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What do you think\Nyou're doing, Matsumoto?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.42,0:12:27.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Slapping my head like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.50,0:12:31.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! If you keep it up,\NI'm going to tell Yachiru.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.90,0:12:36.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...come on...listen...\NDon't do that, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.50,0:12:40.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You should have listened\Nto me to begin with!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.30,0:12:42.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The rest of you,\Ndon't dawdle, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.34,0:12:45.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time we all left,\Nyou blockheads!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.46,0:12:48.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not including me when\Nyou say "blockheads," are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.46,0:12:52.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, of course not...\NYou're not one of them, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.34,0:12:56.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Lately, Captain, your persecution complex\Nhas been showing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.66,0:13:03.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a naughty uniform, Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.82,0:13:09.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...is this guy okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.86,0:13:12.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind him!\NNow, time to withdraw!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.38,0:13:20.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If you lie around like that,\Nyou look like a fixture, Mr. Asano.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.38,0:13:23.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still being formal...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.34,0:13:26.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,KUROSAKI CLINIC
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.82,0:13:43.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sister...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.34,0:13:47.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't changed, have you, Kon?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.58,0:13:53.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This stomping foot\Nhasn't changed, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.42,0:13:55.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This is, without a doubt, Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.06,0:13:59.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I...I am so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.50,0:14:02.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit fooling around.\NHurry up and go on in, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.82,0:14:05.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This little room hasn't changed, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.22,0:14:08.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit it, will you?\NLeave off the "little."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.94,0:14:10.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't compare this with\NByakuya's place!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.46,0:14:14.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry... It just slipped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.38,0:14:18.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, right...\NHey! Don't sit on my bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.46,0:14:21.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, why not?\NGee, you're stingy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.18,0:14:23.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!\NYou can just sit on the floor, idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.90,0:14:26.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,- Boy, you're so stingy...\N- What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.14,0:14:29.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I wondered why no one\Nwas downstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.62,0:14:32.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you two doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.06,0:14:37.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shh! This is terrible!\NIchigo's brought a girl home!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.78,0:14:38.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He brought a girl home
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.86,0:14:40.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,back when he was in\Nmiddle school too, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.54,0:14:42.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Like Tatsuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.30,0:14:44.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not like Tatsuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.18,0:14:49.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,She's more...uh...girlie!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.22,0:14:54.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Tatsuki's gotten more curves since\Nshe entered high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.30,0:14:55.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.74,0:14:59.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you start slobbering, Stupid Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.50,0:15:03.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, as long as he doesn't bring\Nhome someone at Orihime's level,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.94,0:15:05.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.58,0:15:07.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Humph! Karin!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.42,0:15:09.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! There's no way\NIchigo would be so popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.70,0:15:12.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit all the racket, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.46,0:15:14.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,See, he got mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.30,0:15:16.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.22,0:15:20.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Humph!\NGetting all excited at my expense...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.10,0:15:23.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Your family's just as funny as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.46,0:15:24.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.86,0:15:28.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind that. Just tell me\Nwhat the heck an Arrancar is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.26,0:15:29.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.22,0:15:32.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are we being targeted?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.46,0:15:34.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.58,0:15:38.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? That voice?! Renji?!\NWhere are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.54,0:15:43.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to know about that,\Nwe'll tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.42,0:15:45.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.74,0:15:52.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, Ichigo! Long time no see...\Nwell, maybe not.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.70,0:15:57.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys... What have you done\Nto my room light? Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.14,0:16:01.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you'd see the light!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.46,0:16:02.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.94,0:16:07.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, don't get all serious like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.22,0:16:09.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's try to enjoy all this, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.54,0:16:18.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That uniform is\Na dangerous weapon, Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.62,0:16:24.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the latest fad?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.42,0:16:26.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No, he's always like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.38,0:16:30.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,INTERNAL MEDICINE / PEDIATRICS\NKUROSAKI CLINIC
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.74,0:16:34.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The Arrancars are a group of Hollows\Nthat have removed their masks,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.38,0:16:37.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and have gained the powers\Nof both Hollows and Soul Reapers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.42,0:16:41.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Until recently,\Nthey were few and imperfect
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.46,0:16:44.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,but now that Aizen, with his Hogyoku,\Nhas come into contact with them,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.26,0:16:46.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,mature Arrancar have been born.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.86,0:16:50.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what those two\Nwere the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.82,0:16:52.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're with us so far?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.34,0:16:53.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.74,0:16:56.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If not for the sketchbook\NI'd understand it better.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.82,0:17:00.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,In the beginning,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.86,0:17:03.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Soul Society planned to take\Na wait-and-see attitude
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.42,0:17:05.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,until Aizen decided to take matters\Ninto his own hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.22,0:17:08.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,On our side,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.26,0:17:10.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,three of our captains pulled out\Nand went over to the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.46,0:17:14.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, things were in an uproar\Ndue to that Bount incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.74,0:17:21.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But meanwhile, the Arrancars were\Ncompleted quicker than we expected
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.34,0:17:25.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and they were sent into this world,\Nso we couldn't sit back any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.34,0:17:30.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's when\Nwe were quickly selected.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.42,0:17:32.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Who made the selections?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.66,0:17:34.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,General Captain Yamamoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.10,0:17:38.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The Central 46 has been vacant\Nsince Aizen eliminated the leaders.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.30,0:17:40.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,During its vacancy,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.82,0:17:42.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,the General Captain has\Nthe decision-making authority.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.18,0:17:47.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So, the one who knows you best,\NRukia, was chosen...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.26,0:17:50.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I was chosen for my abilities!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.94,0:17:53.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And out of the combatants\Nthey could mobilize,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.38,0:17:56.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I was selected for being\Nthe closest to Rukia.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.10,0:18:00.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I was told to choose
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.38,0:18:04.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,those other than the captains\Nthat I trusted most,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.22,0:18:06.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,so I asked Ikkaku to accompany me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.82,0:18:13.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Then Yumichika said\Nhe had to come along and
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.46,0:18:15.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rangiku, who heard the uproar,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.70,0:18:17.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,said she wanted to come\Nbecause it sounded interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.46,0:18:21.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rangiku wouldn't be swayed,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.10,0:18:24.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,so Captain Hitsugaya was forced\Nto come along to supervise.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.58,0:18:25.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And so we're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.06,0:18:27.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this a picnic?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.42,0:18:35.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway... Aizen's definitely got\Nhis eye on you, Ichigo Kurosaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.42,0:18:37.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Aha! It's Captain Hitsugaya,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.34,0:18:40.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,the only one who refused to go up\Ninto the ceiling with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.98,0:18:42.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you waiting up on\Nthe roof all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.46,0:18:44.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not good!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.70,0:18:47.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You know how you stand out like\Na silver-haired elementary student.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.26,0:18:48.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.26,0:18:52.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that an Arrancar is born
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.34,0:18:54.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,when the mask is removed\Nfrom a Hollow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.54,0:18:58.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But removing the mask of\Nyour run-of-the-mill Hollow
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.30,0:19:00.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,wouldn't get you much\Nof anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.46,0:19:04.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're serious about declaring war\Non Soul Society
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.50,0:19:09.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,it'll naturally be something greater\Nthan the Menos.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.06,0:19:11.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Greater than the Menos?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.38,0:19:14.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What? That sounds like you're saying
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.46,0:19:16.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,there are Hollows stronger\Nthan the Menos.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.38,0:19:20.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... Well, more precisely,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.78,0:19:24.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,there are three classes within\Nthe Menos.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.46,0:19:29.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The first is the "Gillian,"\Nthe lowest class within the Menos,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.34,0:19:30.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and they are many.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.86,0:19:34.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Their characteristic is that\Nthey all look the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.30,0:19:39.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The Hollow you banished\Nin this world,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.42,0:19:41.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,soon after you gained the power\Nof a Soul Reaper was of this kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.38,0:19:43.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you could call them\Nthe small fry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.82,0:19:48.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That one...was a small fry?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.86,0:19:51.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They're huge,\Nbut their movements are sluggish
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.66,0:19:53.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and they are no more intelligent\Nthan beasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.18,0:19:56.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't take much for\Na captain to kill one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.50,0:19:58.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The problem begins with\Nthe next level.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.86,0:20:01.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The second class is the "Adjuchas."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.94,0:20:04.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They're somewhat smaller\Nthan the Gillians,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.54,0:20:06.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and there are fewer of them,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.18,0:20:09.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,but they are highly intelligent and\Nmuch better fighters than the Gillians.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.42,0:20:12.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They control the large numbers\Nof Gillians.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.46,0:20:17.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And the third are the Vasto Lordes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.10,0:20:19.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They are the top class within\Nthe Menos.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.94,0:20:22.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They are equal to humans in size.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.58,0:20:28.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There are said to be only a few of them\Nwithin Hueco Mundo, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.02,0:20:31.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give it to you straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.54,0:20:36.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,These Vasto Lordes are stronger\Nthan our Soul Reaper captains!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.38,0:20:39.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The power gained by the Menos
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.38,0:20:43.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,by turning into Arrancars is\Nan unknown quantity.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.50,0:20:50.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But now that three of our captains\Nhave defected to lead the Menos,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.50,0:20:51.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,this is a fact...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.34,0:20:57.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If Aizen now has more than\Nten of these Vasto Lordes
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.54,0:20:59.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,under his control...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.18,0:21:06.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be the end of Soul Society.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.42,0:21:32.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We have returned...Lord Aizen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.02,0:21:39.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back... Ulquiorra... Yammy...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.34,0:21:46.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, tell me of your achievements\Nin front of your 20 brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.10,0:22:07.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I met you at age 16
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.54,0:22:13.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and we had\Nan eternal love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.22,0:22:18.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Beneath\Ncherry blossoms petals
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.74,0:22:24.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,gently fluttering downward
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.10,0:22:29.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That steep and sunny hill
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.58,0:22:35.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,where I ran up to see you,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.22,0:22:40.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,...And our shadows at\Nthe corner of the park,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.14,0:22:46.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,they are still unchanged\Neven today
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.54,0:22:52.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You, me,\Nand cherry blossom days,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.38,0:22:57.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,we dance\Nand sway in the wind
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.58,0:23:03.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Holding in our heart\Nthe unseen future,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.22,0:23:11.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,we look up at the pink sky
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.41,0:23:21.29,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,In the next episode,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.29,0:23:24.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I will hold a dinner show at my palace\Nin Hueco Mundo.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.68,0:23:27.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You can look forward to\NUlquiorra's report
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.04,0:23:28.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,on the World of the Living.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.90,0:23:30.95,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I am at your service, Lord Aizen.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.95,0:23:33.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... Where will it be held?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.61,0:23:35.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That is a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.24,0:23:36.21,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Illustrated Guide to Soul Reapers!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.07,0:23:41.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Tetsuzaemon...for a long time now...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.38,0:23:44.75,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't received any orders to\Ngo to the World of the Living...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.75,0:23:45.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.94,0:23:47.07,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.48,0:23:51.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,it takes a very serious situation\Nto warrant sending a captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.97,0:23:54.05,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I have even prepared a gigai
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.05,0:23:56.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,so that I can go to the World of\Nthe Living at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.37,0:24:00.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Komamura's gigai...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.52,0:24:03.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.65,0:24:05.09,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...